聆听 Guns N' Roses 贝斯手 Duff McKagan 对 David Bowie 的《Heroes》的激动人心的翻唱https://www.nme.com/news/music/hear-guns-n-roses-bassist-duff-mckagans-rousing-cover-of-david-bowies-heroes-3797881?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=hear-枪炮与玫瑰乐队贝斯手达夫·麦卡甘斯激动人心的大卫·鲍伊斯英雄翻唱Laura MolloyFri, 27 Sep 2024 20:09:17 +0000 Music NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3797881 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Duff-McKagan-and-David-Bowie.-CREDIT_-Cindy-Ord_Getty-Images-for-NYFW_-The-Shows-and-Evan-Agostini_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Duff-McKagan-and-David-Bowie.-CREDIT_-Cindy-Ord_Getty-Images-for-NYFW_-The-Shows-and-Evan-Agostini_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Duff-McKagan-and-David-Bowie.-CREDIT_-Cindy-Ord_Getty-Images-for-NYFW_-The-Shows-and-Evan-Agostini_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Duff-McKagan-and-David-Bowie.-CREDIT_-Cindy-Ord_Getty-Images-for-NYFW_-The-Shows-and-Evan-Agostini_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Duff-McKagan-and-David-Bowie.-CREDIT_-Cindy-Ord_Getty-Images-for-NYFW_-The-Shows-and-Evan-Agostini_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Duff-McKagan-and-David-Bowie.-CREDIT_-Cindy-Ord_Getty-Images-for-NYFW_-The-Shows-and-Evan-Agostini_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Duff-McKagan-and-David-Bowie.-CREDIT_-Cindy-Ord_Getty-Images-for-NYFW_-The-Shows-and-Evan-Agostini_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>他将于下周开始他的“灯塔”巡演</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/hear-guns-n-roses-bassist-duff-mckagans-rousing-cover-of-david-bowies-heroes-3797881">《Hear Guns N&#39; Roses》之后的贝斯手 Duff McKagan 翻唱的 David Bowie 的《Heroes》令人振奋，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Duff-McKagan-and-David-Bowie.-CREDIT_-Cindy-Ord_Getty-Images-for-NYFW_-The-Shows-and-Evan-Agostini_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Duff-McKagan-and-David-Bowie.-CREDIT_-Cindy-Ord_Getty-Images-for-NYFW_-The-Shows-and-Evan-Agostini_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Duff-McKagan-and-David-Bowie.-CREDIT_-Cindy-Ord_Getty-Images-for-NYFW_-The-Shows-and-Evan-Agostini_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Duff-McKagan-and-David-Bowie.-CREDIT_-Cindy-Ord_Getty-Images-for-NYFW_-The-Shows-and-Evan-Agostini_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Duff-McKagan-and-David-Bowie.-CREDIT_-Cindy-Ord_Getty-Images-for-NYFW_-The-Shows-and-Evan-Agostini_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Duff-McKagan-and-David-Bowie.-CREDIT_-Cindy-Ord_Getty-Images-for-NYFW_-The-Shows-and-Evan-Agostini_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Duff-McKagan-and-David-Bowie.-CREDIT_-Cindy-Ord_Getty-Images-for-NYFW_-The-Shows-and-Evan-Agostini_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/duff-mckagan">达夫·麦卡根 (Duff McKagan)</a>在下周开始的“灯塔”巡演之前分享了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/david-bowie">大卫·鲍伊 (David Bowie)</a>的《英雄》翻唱作品。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/guns-n-roses-live-at-glastonbury-photos-setlist-3460919">枪与玫瑰乐队在格拉斯顿伯里现场表演：一场精彩的表演......给了错误的观众</a></strong></li></ul><p>继去年年底发行个人专辑《Lighthouse》后，这位<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/guns-n-roses">枪炮玫瑰</a>乐队的贝斯手正在欧洲、英国和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/guns-n-roses-duff-mckagan-announces-solo-us-tour-shares-new-concert-video-3761518">美国</a>进行<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/guns-n-roses-duff-mckagan-announces-2024-uk-and-european-solo-tour-buy-tickets-3618102">一系列演出</a>。巡演将于周一（9 月 30 日）在都柏林拉开帷幕，并将于 10 月在伦敦、华沙、柏林、米兰、巴黎等地停留，然后于下个月前往美国。</p><p>在登上舞台之前，麦卡根发布了鲍伊 1977 年热门单曲的翻唱版。 “我们认为在灯塔巡演前夕在这里推出几首新鲜歌曲是个好主意，”他在 Instagram 上写道。 “选择大卫·鲍伊的英雄对我来说似乎是一个自然的主题（当然，我是一个巨大的历史书呆子）......70 年代中期冷战时期柏林墙阴影下的不幸恋人。”</p><p>除了《英雄》之外，麦卡根还分享了一首新歌《True To The Death Rock N Roll Ballad》，他说自己写这首歌是为了“尝试和赞美”《英雄》所描绘的时代。这首华丽摇滚歌曲探讨了爱、欲望和时间的主题。查看下面的两条曲目。 </p><p><iframe title="Duff McKagan - 英雄 - 官方展示台" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/4Ps6q3uw-OU?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe title="至死不渝摇滚民谣" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ulnw2D3JyY4?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> 《Lighthouse》是麦卡根作为独唱艺术家的第三张专辑，继 1993 年的首张专辑《Believe In Me》和 2019 年的《Tenderness》之后。客串演出的还有<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/iggy-pop">Iggy Pop</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/alice-in-chains">Alice In Chains</a>吉他手 Jerry Cantrell 和枪炮与玫瑰乐队的长期乐队成员<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/slash">Slash</a> 。</p><p>您可以在下面查看完整的巡演日期列表，并<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fduff-mckagan-tickets%2Fartist%2F5214854" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>查找英国和欧洲日期的门票，以及<a href="https://www.ticketmaster.com/duff-mckagan-tickets/artist/1311767?irgwc=1&amp;clickid=RgHWNZyYUxyKTIqQnV04UVzBUkCyYiRxgw1XSc0&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;impradid=2862475&amp;REFERRAL_ID=tmfeedbuyat2862475&amp;wt.mc_id=aff_BUYAT_2862475&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;impradname=NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;ircid=4272" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处查找</a>美国日期的门票。</p><h2> Duff McKagan 2024 年美国巡演日期为：</h2><p><strong>九月</strong><br /><strong>30 – 都柏林学院，爱尔兰都柏林</strong></p><p><strong>十月</strong><br /><strong>2 – 车库，格拉斯哥，苏格兰</strong><br /><strong>3 – 曼彻斯特学院，英国曼彻斯特</strong><br /><strong>5 – 英国伦敦伊斯灵顿议会厅</strong><br /><strong>7 – 荷兰乌得勒支蒂沃利弗雷登堡</strong><br /><strong>8 – 德国科隆 Die Kantine</strong><br /> <strong>9 – 德国慕尼黑Freiheitshalle</strong><br /> <strong>11 – 捷克共和国布尔诺索诺中心</strong><br /><strong>13 – 斯托多拉俱乐部，华沙，波兰</strong><br /><strong>14 – 德国柏林新克尔恩海马港</strong><br /><strong>16 – Magazzini Generali，米兰，意大利</strong><br /><strong>17 – Kulturfabrik Kofmehl，瑞士索洛图恩</strong><br /><strong>19 – OM，比利时列日</strong><br /><strong>20 – 法国巴黎特里亚农宫</strong><br /><strong>22 - 纳伦，斯德哥尔摩，瑞典</strong></p><p><strong>十一月</strong><br /><strong>4 – 天堂摇滚俱乐部，波士顿，马萨诸塞州</strong><br /><strong>6 – 红泊松，纽约，纽约</strong><br /><strong>8 – Outset，伊利诺伊州芝加哥</strong><br /><strong>10 – 蓝鸟酒店，科罗拉多州丹佛市</strong><br /><strong>13 – 雷伊剧院，洛杉矶，加利福尼亚州</strong><br /><strong>18 - 阿拉丁剧院，俄勒冈州波特兰</strong><br /><strong>20 – The Showbox，西雅图，华盛顿</strong></p><p>在其他新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/guns-n-roses-duff-mckagan-says-the-simpsons-should-own-up-to-using-his-name-as-inspiration-for-duff-beer-3765766">这位贝斯手最近公开了<em>《辛普森一家》</em>的故事，</a>据报道，该动画系列的虚构啤酒品牌达夫啤酒使用了他的名字。然而，他的说法<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/the-simpsons-writer-shoots-down-duff-mckagan-claim-inspired-duff-beer-3766554">后来被节目的编剧和制片人驳回</a>。</p><p>三月份，麦卡根分享了伊基·波普（Iggy Pop）在他十几岁的时候如何帮助他度过了一次<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/guns-n-roses-iggy-pop-got-me-through-a-bad-mushroom-trip-3601948">“糟糕的蘑菇之旅”</a> 。他在播客上说：“我去看了一场 Iggy 秀，蘑菇吃得太多了，我以为我得去医院，吓坏了。”</p><p> “我从头到尾看完了《伊基》，迷幻药太多了。但他让我失望了。我已经是伊基的忠实粉丝了，但后来我想，他对我来说意义更大。他是我人生的一个转折点。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com