音乐场馆信托基金的 #OwnOurVenues 计划拯救了斯旺西的 The Bunkhouse https://www.nme.com/news/music/swanseas-the-bunkhouse-saved-by-music-venue-trusts-ownourvenues-scheme-3797869?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=swanseas-the-bunkhouse-saved-按音乐场馆信托拥有我们的场馆计划Laura MolloyFri, 27 Sep 2024 19:02:52 +0000 Music NewsNewsLive Music News https://www.nme.com/?p=3797869 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Bunkhouse-Swansea.-CREDIT_-Press.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Bunkhouse-Swansea.-CREDIT_-Press.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Bunkhouse-Swansea.-CREDIT_-Press-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Bunkhouse-Swansea.-CREDIT_-Press-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Bunkhouse-Swansea.-CREDIT_-Press-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Bunkhouse-Swansea.-CREDIT_-Press-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Bunkhouse-Swansea.-CREDIT_-Press-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这是该突破性计划购买和保护的第三个场馆</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/swanseas-the-bunkhouse-saved-by-music-venue-trusts-ownourvenues-scheme-3797869">由 Music Venue Trust 的 #OwnOurVenues 计划保存的斯旺西 The Bunkhouse</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Bunkhouse-Swansea.-CREDIT_-Press.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Bunkhouse-Swansea.-CREDIT_-Press.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Bunkhouse-Swansea.-CREDIT_-Press-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Bunkhouse-Swansea.-CREDIT_-Press-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Bunkhouse-Swansea.-CREDIT_-Press-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Bunkhouse-Swansea.-CREDIT_-Press-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Bunkhouse-Swansea.-CREDIT_-Press-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> The Bunkhouse 是斯旺西的一个草根音乐场所，是音乐场所信托基金会 #OwnOurVenues 计划拯救的最新一个。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/2023-was-worst-year-for-venue-closures-while-no-one-in-music-industry-seems-to-care-say-mvt-3562266">MVT 表示，2023 年是“场馆关闭最糟糕的一年”，而“音乐行业似乎没有人关心”</a></strong></li></ul><p>该计划于<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/music-venue-trust-launch-scheme-to-purchase-uks-grassroots-music-venues-3229623" target="_blank" rel="noopener">2022 年</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/music-venue-trust-launch-scheme-to-purchase-uks-grassroots-music-venues-3229623">5 月首次由 Music Venue Trust 透露，</a>一年后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/own-our-venues-campaign-succeeds-in-securing-first-funding-for-mvt-to-start-buying-uk-grassroots-gig-spaces-3424496">该慈善机构通过一系列捐赠和投资筹集了 230 万英镑，</a>并宣布取得成功。它被称为“国家信托，但针对场馆”，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ed-sheeran-backs-music-venue-trusts-own-our-venues-campaign-3316937">得到了 Ed Sheeran 等人的支持</a>，场馆与音乐场馆地产 (MVP) 签署了一份“文化租赁”，保证只要它们作为草根空间运营为当地社区提供现场音乐，他们可以享受使用该建筑的乐趣。</p><p>自从 #OwnOurVenues 宣布以来，由 Music Venue Trust 创建的独立慈善社区福利协会 (CCBS) MVP 已购买了两处房产。去年<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/music-venue-trust-buys-first-venue-under-national-trust-of-venues-public-ownership-scheme-3509198">10 月，阿瑟顿 (Atherton) 的 The Snug 成为第一个受到该计划拯救和保护的酒店</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-ferret-in-preston-saved-by-mvts-own-our-venues-scheme-3755247">紧随其后的是普雷斯顿 (Preston) 的 The Ferret</a> 。</p><p>购买位于斯旺西的 Bunkhouse 是一个可容纳 235 人的现场音乐场所、排练空间和摄影工作室，标志着威尔士第一个被该计划置于永久保护地位的场所。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm