me.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Robert-Smith-performing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Robert-Smith-performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Robert-Smith-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Robert-Smith-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Robert-Smith-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Robert-Smith-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/The-Cure">The Cure</a>乐队的<a href="/artists/Robert-Smith">罗伯特·史密斯</a>(Robert Smith) 讲述了他们对新专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-cure-new-album-songs-of-a-lost-world-interview-update-relentless-tour-3229589">Songs Of A Lost World</a> 》的漫长等待。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/the-cure-interview-robert-smith-big-read-exclusive-interview-glastonbury-40th-anniversary-2019-glastonbury-mad-cool-2524439">大读物 - 独家 - The Cure：“格拉斯顿伯里不会是我今年夏天唯一一次在舞台上泪流满面”</a></strong></li></ul><p>几周来，后朋克传奇人物一直在调侃 2008 年的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-the-cure-9962-342712">4:13 Dream</a> 》的后续作品，首先<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/it-looks-like-the-cure-are-finally-teasing-their-new-album-3791992">改变了他们的在线形象</a>，然后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-cure-send-fans-postcards-confirming-new-album-title-and-release-date-3793374">向粉丝发送暗示专辑名称和发行日期的明信片</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-cure-album-poster-appears-in-crawley-pub-where-they-played-their-first-gig-3793696">并在</a>他们在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-cure-album-poster-appears-in-crawley-pub-where-they-played-their-first-gig-3793696">克劳利酒吧</a>进行了他们的第一场演出，在世界各地的城市<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/are-the-cure-teasing-a-songs-of-a-lost-world-event-in-blackpool-3795230">进行了投影</a>，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-cure-launch-secret-songs-of-a-lost-world-website-and-whatsapp-channel-3794283">推出了一个秘密网站和 WhatsApp 频道</a>，随后让歌迷们<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-a-snippet-of-the-cures-comeback-single-alone-3795730">简短地品尝了他们的新单曲《Alone</a> 》。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-cure-alone-listen-full-song-album-songs-of-a-lost-world-details-pre-order-3797210">这首单曲标志着他们 16 年来的首张单曲发行后</a>，乐队还确认他们的第 14 张专辑《Songs Of A Lost World》将于 11 月 1 日发行，现在可以<a href="https://thecure.lnk.to/SongsOfALostWorld" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>预购。</p><p>现在，在乐队官方 Instagram 帐户上分享的一段视频中，谈到等待他们的新 LP 时，Smtih 分享道：“我不认为这张专辑真的有一种正式的开始，因为它一直在漂流，从我的生活中消失了很长一段时间。我的意思是，如果我有一个遗憾的话，那就是我在 2019 年说了任何关于这件事的事情，因为我真的不应该那样做。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DAbLQ_GISn0/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#0000